{"id":288942,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-上海邬玉萍等4人希望得到公安局长接待被/","date":"2013-04-13T17:45:51Z","modified":"2013-04-13T17:45:51Z","title":"维权网 | 上海邬玉萍等4人希望得到公安局长接待被拘留（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>时</span><span>，上海市公安局局长白少康到凉城新村凉城派出所视察工作，接待市民，倾听民情。上海数百上访维权人士闻讯，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>点开始陆续赶到凉城新村凉城派出所等候白局长的到来，欲向他倾诉多年的冤屈。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>结果令上访维权人士们非常失望，不但没有见到白少康局长，反而被送府村路黑监狱关押失去人身自由。上访维权人士邬玉萍、游宇虹、张洪祥、江莉等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>人被凉城派出所绑架后遭到行政拘留。到了晚上，被关押在府村路黑监狱里上访维权人士释放出来返回凉城派出所静坐抗议，要求释放邬玉萍、游宇虹、张洪祥、江莉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>邬玉萍房屋被强拆后开始上访维权，曾经被劳教一年零三个月。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>徐汇区访民张洪祥住在徐汇区东安二村小区，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月因相邻纠纷，遭到上海公安局徐汇分局枫林派出所民警钱明假公济私，包庇有钱有势的肇事者。警察伪造询问笔录，助纣为虐在第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">53</span><span>天将已近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span><span>岁的受害人张洪祥抓进看守所关押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>天。这次张洪祥来到凉城派出所是希望得到白少康局长接待倾诉冤情，没想到见不到白局长反而被拘留。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>有关</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>人被行政拘留的详细情况，本网将会继续追踪关注。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>邬玉萍</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13817134751</span></div>\n<div><span>张洪祥</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13671857663</span></div>\n<div><span>江莉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13661736430</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-JhLCEmmdSGM/UWmBxOc7A4I/AAAAAAAAgUQ/0tPkLjwtcdo/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE02.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"226\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-JhLCEmmdSGM/UWmBxOc7A4I/AAAAAAAAgUQ/0tPkLjwtcdo/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE02.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}